Title: Viessmann Flow & Return Isolation Valve (Single)
Description: A Viessmann brand replacement single flow and return isolation valve. It also allows the user to stop the flow in case of a leak or emergency. Title: Rothenberger Rocal Pro 2 61197R rocal pro 2 flushing pump
Description: Designed to work with systems of up to 40 radiators over three storeys, the Rothenberger Rocal Pro 2 power flusher has an ultra-high flow rate and instant flow reverse.
